quran[13{c,v,t}:
19,26,Fakulee washrabee wa qarree 'ainaa; fa immaa tarayinnna minal bashari ahadan faqooleee innee nazartu lir Rahmaani sawman falan ukallimal yawma insiyyaa
19,27,Fa atat bihee qawmahaa tahmiluhoo qaaloo yaa Maryamoo laqad ji'ti shai'an fariyyaa
19,28,Yaaa ukkhta Haaroona maa kaana abokim ra-a saw'inw wa maa kaanat ummuki baghiyyaa
19,29,Fa ashaarat ilaih; qaaloo kaifa nukallimu man kaana fil mahdi sabiyyaa
19,30,Qaala innee 'abdullaahi aataaniyal Kitaaba wa ja'alanee Nabiyyaa
19,31,Wa ja'alanee mubaarakan aina maa kuntu wa awsaanee bis Salaati waz Zakaati maa dumtu haiyaa
19,32,Wa barram biwaalidatee wa lam yaj'alnee jabbaaran shaqiyyaa
19,33,Wassalaamu 'alaiya yawma wulittu wa yawma amootu wa yawma ub'asu baiyaa
19,34,Zaalika 'Eesab-nu Marya; qawlal haqqil lazee feehi yamtaroon
19,35,Maa kaana lillaahi ai yattakhiza minw waladin Subhaanah; izaa qadaaa amran fa innamaa yaqoolu lahoo kun fa yakoon
19,36,Wa innal laaha Rabbee wa Rabbukum fa'budooh; haazaa Siraatum Mustaqeem
19,37,Fakhtalafal ahzaabu mim bainihim fawailul lillazeena kafaroo mim mashhadi Yawmin 'azeem
19,38,Asmi' bihim wa absir Yawma yaatoonanaa laakiniz zaalimoonal yawma fee dalaalim mubeen
